Class Info

java.lang.Object
  zeus.rete.Info
public class Info
extends java.lang.Object

simple storage class - used to shuttle information between various nodes on various graphs. Was a package protected local class in ConflicSet, but I decided that it was best exposed and refactored before I went mad.
